{
  "texts": [
    "It is crucial to identify and minimize the risks of such leaks and develop strategies to address these concerns with future models.",
    "This has long been a concern in applying language models to healthcare (35).",
    "Prior to the advent of LLMs, BERT-based models were typically combined with differential privacy training and federated learning strategies to better protect privacy in healthcare applications (36).",
    "Privacy and data protection regulation compliance is another significant concern associated with LLMs.",
    "These models have the capacity to \"memorize\" personal information, putting it at risk of being discovered by other users or potential attackers (37, 38)."
  ]
}